seoDescription.seoDescription:
Located in Denverâ€™s charming Central Park neighborhood (formerly Stapleton),  and just a 15 minute drive from downtown Denver, Solana Central Park features 307  pet-friendly, rental apartments. Residents can choose from nine different floor plans that range from studios to two-bedroom options.

With over 22,000 square feet of curated amenities, Solana Central Park offers a resort-style swiming pool and spa with shaded cabanas, an indoor/outdoor, luxury health and fitness center with private workout studios, and a coworking space with individual workspaces and conference rooms.  Other useful amenities include a pet spa, resident parcel pending to ensure safe delivery of your packages, on-site management, bike storage and repair facilities, secure garage parking, and EV charging stations. Residents will also enjoy the luxury of over 1,000 acres of nearby parks and open space, coupled with 60 miles of trails for biking and walking- all of this and more, set against the stunning backdrop of the Colorado Rocky Mountains.
